### if you make changes and you want to upload the changes/files/dir to gitbug
git status
git add .  (### . for all or put the name of the file)
git commit -m " add description here"
git push origin main ## here use password and tocken gotten from github

### if you made changes in github and you wnat to pull them to local PC
git fectch all
git diff origin/main ## to check the the changes
git pull 

### you can also install aplication github-desktop for userfriendly GUI